extends layout.pug

block content

  article.portfolio-intro

    h1 Peace Be Upon You

    p My portfolio contains projects that have all of it's functionality and Javascript coded by me. Projects displayed on this page are a random quote generator, pagination of data from an object, a responsive web form, an object oriented programmed game show app coded with ES6 syntax, and an app that displays/filters data from randomapi.

  article.portfolio-project-thumbs
    .projects-box.box.grid

      each project in projects
        
        a.cell(href=`/projects/${project.id}`)
          img.thumbnail(src=`${project.image_url[0]}` alt=`${project.project_name} image`)
          h5= project.project_name

